# Acronyms

| Acronym | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| **SMFACN** | **Stage Min Files and Commit New** — stage only the smallest set of files that belong to the change (avoid unrelated edits), then create a **new** commit with an appropriate message. |

When the user writes **SMFACN**, follow that workflow unless they specify otherwise.

